{"tid":697144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦盧建民即將判刑","createTime":"2018-06-10T17:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T15:16:07.000Z","uid":40819,"like":55,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7eecb6353fdb09b18fd7ee2a3f07dc5bd0a64d","tid":697144,"uid":40819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/005429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F005429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d41644f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瞓醒後，梁天琦同盧建民朝早就會接受判刑<br />\n兩人各一項暴動罪罪成<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴動罪最高可以囚10年<br />\n而之前一班義士之中最高係囚4年9個月</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，梁天琦同兩名被告李諾文、林傲軒之前有一項暴動罪未達成有效裁決<br />\n律政司亦會正式提出重審<br />\n<br />\n形勢兇險，希望大家集集氣。"},{"pid":"7ca391aaf31a64b98b9a19be1f54bafc884c8f2e","tid":697144,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe82a5c974a78675e0f270e753517352d2a6de8","tid":697144,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af646ca6a92f2f400752a6b964a01e18294f7f68","tid":697144,"uid":38216,"like":13,"dislike":21,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少咗一個，出返嚟唔好走咁前"},{"pid":"8f78c22551e9e4339727126216b8a649a9f5ad1b","tid":697144,"uid":40819,"like":23,"dislike":8,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"af646ca6a92f2f400752a6b964a01e18294f7f68","tid":697144,"uid":38216,"like":13,"dislike":21,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年<i